Create Slicers 10

Create the following Slicers;

District

Crime type

Quater

Month

Steps

Select Slicer visual

Go to the Fields pane

Drag and Drop District Name into the Field pane

Drag and drop Primary Type into the Field pane

Drag and drop Quater into the Field pane

Drag and drop Month into the Field pane

Go to the Format pane, Off Slicer header and  On the Title, type in Title text and change the Background color.
